<td width="600" colspan="4">
<b>Description</b><br>
Gossamer is a step up in the chain of caster armor. It is better armor class than Damask and Woven and also very lightweight. Common places where gossimer armor is dropped: 
<br><br>
<li> Festering Hags in Estate of Unrest 
<li> Magicians in Nejena 
<li> Goblin Wizard in Permafrost 
<li> Necromancers in Befallen</td>
